然保护区昆虫的丰富性、多样性，更彰显了永安天宝岩管理局长期致力自然保护的突出成效。福建发现全球新物种：天宝岩肿腿迷甲"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-9805365705c73bf507d5121ee7b0a527_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/535999255"}}, "attached_info": "ClUI2PX4vPGKyeB7EAMaCDgxMzkyODgxIMu26pQGMAI4kAFAL3IJNTM1OTk5MjU1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "48_1654326378.4647133", "card_id": "Q_535939693", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 48}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价周深和张韶涵的合作舞台《一路生花》？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-d8ec208d418e2be1ed37399339acd2bc_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/535939693"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I2PX4vPGKyeB7EAMaCDgxMzc5NjEwILOp6JQGMAc4PkAwcgk1MzU5Mzk2OTN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "49_1654326378.4651692", "card_id": "Q_535900191", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 60}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "6 月 3 日台湾新增本土确诊病例 76517 例，新增死亡病例 142 例，目前当地疫情形势如何？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "台湾地区流行疫情指挥中心 6 月 3 日公布，台湾地区新增 76517 例新冠肺炎本土确诊病例，新增死亡病例 142 例，新增中重症病例 409 例，另有输入病例 47 例。台湾新增本土确诊病例 76517 例，新增死亡病例 142 例"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-d9421f5c501e8e20c73c07be850cdefa_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/535900191"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I2PX4vPGKyeB7EAMaCDgxMzcwODAzINff5pQG